Module count
Package count.model

Class MLGamma

java.lang.Object
count.model.ML
count.model.MLMixedRate
count.model.MLGamma
public class MLGamma
extends MLMixedRate
Maximum likelihood for GammaInvariant model using rate and shape parameters. Not really robust: may croak with very large rate classes implied by skewed multipliers.
